{"tid":595193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 夜蒲女中環兜巴星警員 涉襲警被捕","createTime":"2018-03-16T12:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T12:52:04.000Z","uid":34701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7c080a1872743a9cdaa2d53f9b131620c98a3233","tid":595193,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T12:23:13.000Z","msg":"中環一間酒吧外昨晚發生襲警事件！據悉，昨晚約11時15分，有人報案稱中環雪廠街一間酒吧，一名女子與職員發生爭執，其間職員要求她離開，但對方拒絶，且不斷在吵鬧，於是報警。警員接報到場了解，惟該女子情緒仍然相當激動，更涉嫌掌摑一名軍裝警員。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》取得一段短片，全長僅5秒，畫面是經過翻拍的，目前在社交平台瘋傳。片段中，明顯看到一名身穿白色小背心、牛仔褲的短髮女子，情緒相當高漲，並大大聲面對着一名軍裝男警員高聲呼叫，惟片段為翻拍，聲音相當嘈雜，難以聽清楚內容，只見該女子咆哮後高舉左手「手指指」，男警員企圖讓她冷靜之際，冷不防被女子兜巴星了右邊臉頰，「啪」聲震天，警員立即以手撫面，片段即告中斷。<br />\n<br />\n記者向警方發言人了解，得知警方以襲警罪拘捕涉事的35歲姓伊女子，事件仍需進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180316/large/1521201710_46f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180316%2Flarge%2F1521201710_46f6.jpg&h=e0f6bfef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180316/57956676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180316%2F57956676&d=5uofD5zaLSkMlb4KObmcrGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=485ece2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180316%2F57956676&h=f67b4ed3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180316/57956676</a>"},{"pid":"9eb3c76007c1d14caaa4f9af1e727ffa1cd6f51c","tid":595193,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T12:25:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gKqS8TNbgJk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgKqS8TNbgJk&d=5uofD5zaLSkMlb4KObmcrGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5d2837e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gKqS8TNbgJk</a>"},{"pid":"c444e5292c169b9b2a02a92ebb0fd938a1fee255","tid":595193,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T12:52:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}